    "## 6. Step-wise Accuracy Gap\n",
    "\n",
    "We compute the accuracy gap between Track B and Track A at each common validation step."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1200x600 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
